com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.linearpathmatch.split
Class QuantizedPath

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.linearpathmatch.split.QuantizedPath
public class QuantizedPath
extends java.lang.Object

Discretizes a FlatPath quantized by a Minimum Segment Length. Allows referring to locations along the path by discrete QuantumIndexes. Quantizing a path during splitting allows maintaining the invariant:

  • Introduced nodes must be separated from path vertices by at least the Minimum Segment Length
